nage multiple toasts with stacking.\n\n2. **UIIconButton**: Should extend Contai
ner, have a background (square), icon (text or texture), optional label below. S
upport pulse animation. Similar hover/click interactions as UIButton but circula
r/square icon style.\n\n3. **UISegmentedControl**: Should extend Container, have
